<h3 id="7-real-estate-search">7. Real estate search</h3>

<p>Semantic image search is useful for real estate agents, home buyers, and sellers who want to find a home similar to something they already saw and liked. Using a semantic image search, a buyer could upload a photo of a home (or even a specific room) they love to find the closest match in their buying area. This saves the home buyer time wading through pages of available houses and takes some of the stress out of the house-hunting process.</p>

