<h3 id="9-pet-and-animal-search">9. Pet and animal search</h3>

<p>Many people turn to online pet marketplaces to find their furry friends. Many would-be pet owners have an idea in mind of the type of pet (e.g., breed, color, size) they want, but doing a basic search on an online pet adoption website can quickly become overwhelming because of the number of pet listings. With semantic image search, a visitor can use a specific image of an adorable puppy (or another animal) to quickly sort through the database of available pets to find similar matches.</p>

