<h3 id="10-augment-a-museum-experience">10. Augment a museum experience</h3>

<p>Museums have an opportunity to augment their visitors‚Äô experiences by allowing them to snap photos of things they see and then provide them with more information about the object they‚Äôre looking at. After a visitor snaps a photo, a semantic image search uses it to sort through the museum‚Äôs database to locate more information about the relevant object. It then sends this information about the object back to the visitor.</p>

